Dedicated User Login Page (/login)

The tab switcher was removed from the main login page to focus exclusively on Pet Owners (Users) login and signup.
Added a clear Staff Portals redirection section at the bottom of the card with direct links to Doctor Login 🩺 and Admin Login 💼.
Dedicated Doctor Login at /doctor

If an unauthenticated user or non-doctor visits /doctor, the system blocks page loading and displays a dedicated Doctor Workspace Login portal.
This portal includes an autofill helper box populated with default demo credentials (doctor@jacovet.com / doctor123) and a return link to switch back to the Pet Owner login.
Once logged in as a doctor, it displays the clinic patient consult dashboard.
Dedicated Admin Login at /admin

If an unauthenticated user or non-admin visits /admin, the system blocks page loading and displays a dedicated Desk Admin Login portal.
This portal is populated with default demo credentials (admin@jacovet.com / admin123) and a return link to switch back to the Pet Owner login.
Once logged in as an admin, it displays the clinic scheduler queue and invoicing desk.
